Tally Prime Project — XYZ Distributors

This project simulates a full accounting cycle of a trading business. I created the company, configured GST, created stock & ledger masters, entered purchases and sales with GST, recorded expenses, handled returns, performed bank reconciliation, and generated final financial statements.

Quick Steps Completed
  • Company Creation + GST Enable
  • Ledger Master Setup (Capital, Bank, GST, Expenses, Debtors, Creditors)
  • Stock Items & Units Setup
  • Purchase / Sales Entries with GST
  • Payment, Receipt, Contra & Journal Entries
  • Purchase & Sales Return
  • Bank Reconciliation Process
  • Reports: Trial Balance, Profit & Loss, Balance Sheet
